{"tid":1492834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"視點31 被捕之後: 新屋嶺","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:35:44.000Z","uid":263230,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df71257bb2df78ad566605970559ac2bfb7e2042","tid":1492834,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/511059093000065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthk31thisweek%2Fvideos%2F511059093000065%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Pno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=433d908a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/511059093000065/</a><br />\n【被捕之後】<br />\n台劇《我們與惡的距離》有一個情節：「殺人犯李曉明願意與家人見面，但法務部突然宣布李曉明即將被槍決，但他的家人、他的代表律師，都沒有收到通知，最後一面也見不到。」<br />\n<br />\n虛構的情節會在現實發生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n811晚於銅鑼灣、尖沙咀被捕嘅示威者，被送到接近邊境的新屋嶺扣留中心，有律師指等候十多小時仍未見到當事人、有被捕者稱在沒有律師陪同下落口供、有人頭破血流卻等一整晚才被送到醫院&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n警方上星期五，在例行記者會上回應過，表示「手頭無資料」，但相關人士可按機制投訴。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期二（20/8），我們再到記者會詢問，警方承認811當晚有54個被捕人士被帶到新屋嶺，其中31人要送院，6人傷勢較嚴重，包括骨折等。<br />\n至於傷者延遲到醫院、律師被阻撓見當事人等指控，有組織罪案及三合會調查科(O記)高級警司李桂華表示，「要時間睇睇」、「無資料喺手」&hellip;"},{"pid":"f0e012f2e3ed820ba67e37b9b64bead5b6f17604","tid":1492834,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點救佢地出黎"},{"pid":"e1ad2b47cd9ea356fd4ab2da8d2a1a0ff6e62c7e","tid":1492834,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2cb4e966dd8c86945cbe3c82132bc268b3c11c","tid":1492834,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHk6uRB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHk6uRB.png&h=06ae07d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n------------------分界線